'''''Monsters in Hell''''' is a [[ZX Spectrum]] game written by Martin Lewis and released by [[Softek Software|Softek]] in 1983.<ref name="giantlist"/> The player kills wizards by digging holes in the floor to watch them plummet to their death. The screen layout and gameplay are similar to the 1980 Universal arcade game ''[[Space Panic]]''.

